  "1811550": {
    "name": "Forts - High Seas",
    "steam_appid": 1811550,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/7dfbe5ab156ae9fd364660b29a761cde.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=156 /></span><br><br>登上联合海军的战舰、航母和无畏舰出海航行，在《进击！要塞！》的第二个 DLC 中与烦人的海盗展开战斗。全新的水体系统，全新的战役、武器、弹药系统，新的 HUD 与曲目 – “起航远洋”将《进击！要塞！》经典的物理学乐趣延伸到建造、战斗、溅起水花的新层面！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新战役</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/98aaf80ea2aee5ed54b1c0035a45bd4c.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=384 /></span><br>自从著名科学家弗雷德·科派斯特教授在远海上神秘失踪，已经过去了五年时间。现在，他的儿子麦克斯 – 联合海军中的一名船长，在与海盗们的战舰、航母和无畏舰轮番战斗，寻找可怕的超级武器的过程中，寻找有关教授境遇的传言。 <br><br><br><strong>包含内容：</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>16 个拥有独特背景的任务<br></li><li>任务类型多种多样，如：<br>        - 执法行动 - 船舰间的战斗<br>        - 阻截追击 - 摧毁逃离区域的敌方船只<br>        - 登船行动 - 夺取敌方结构的控制权<br>        - 陆海之战 - 陆地要塞与船舰间的战斗<br>        - 航母打击 - 在船舰上起飞战机，轰炸敌人<br></li><li>敌意满满、不断变化的环境<br></li><li>交互式图画小说风格过场<br></li><li>精致的学习线路，教授玩家新的功能，逐个任务解锁各种武器<br></li><li>联合海军 HUD<br></li><li>全新动感曲目</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全新军备</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/4a0e9ea8d936848b30f06e8c3024912c.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>能量穹顶</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>创建一道临时屏障，抵挡可被摧毁的炮弹<br></li><li>建在低处，以防范飞机投下的炸药</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/5ee3a75dd7f63cc6a9b74ecba8eaa97d.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>鱼叉</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发射可以改变蜂群导弹和巨型导弹方向的诱饵弹<br></li><li>发射可以控制中立结构的控制弹</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/956dba2d8c6fb125af12364c92a0731b.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>飞行跑道</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发射霹雳战机<br></li><li>发射夜鹰战机</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/ac32e41d4b71469fb56bf0fc71245dd1.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>承力基座</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可升级为甲板炮<br></li><li>可升级为轨道激光</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/8939e11c8c45981544549ecbf9cc6a4d.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>甲板炮</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发射高爆炮弹<br></li><li>可升级至 2 根和 3 根炮管版本*<br></li><li>*可在集中开火和分散开火之间切换<br></li><li>需要承力基座</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/ee1168759b6240153dc5550c3e332c47.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>轨道激光</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>发射横扫轨道激光弹药<br></li><li>发射聚焦轨道激光弹药<br></li><li>可升级以获取弹轨预览功能<br></li><li>需要承力基座</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >弹药</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/b6aa398b68d07648790b4e7a921d33c2.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>诱饵弹药</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>如松鼠一般。引诱和改变蜂群导弹和巨型导弹的方向<br></li><li>使用鱼叉发射</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/53da47015384b40e85eeeca1cd8515d9.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>控制弹药</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>获取结构的控制权<br></li><li>使用鱼叉发射</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/dde704d38c81e6efba91af99284c32d6.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>霹雳战机</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在预先确定的地点投下多个炸弹<br></li><li>使用飞行跑道发射</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/362adc06aaff46c728d6c0007a1c7933.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>夜鹰战机</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>投掷高渗透力、燃烧性的宝石路精准炸弹<br></li><li>使用飞行跑道发射</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/09d6ac1c4d5192a93cc3b4349f30074f.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>横扫轨道激光</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可以横扫打击点的强力卫星光束<br></li><li>使用轨道激光发射</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/175f0b010f6f363db23ca61b7fa6d528.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=122 /></span><br><strong>聚焦轨道激光弹药</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>可以集中精确打击打击点的强力聚焦卫星光束<br></li><li>使用轨道激光发射</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >水体技术</h2><br>《进击！要塞！》以经典切特有的物理引擎而广为人知，现在追加了全新的水体系统，获得了重大升级。船只会因真实的浮力浮起，如果失衡则会偏向一侧。未连接至反应堆的结构会沉没至海底（除非迅速重新连接上）。海面拥有完整的特效，包括水花飞溅效果、泡泡粒子、水下爆炸和声音效果等。这一技术，将业已令人颇为满意的物理体验游戏玩法和模组制作的可能性推向了全新的世界！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >起航远洋专属内容</h2><br><strong>联合海军 HUD</strong><br>全新的游戏内联合海军 HUD 供您使用！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/b18c46c15a06467087527e037148b61f.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=384 /></span><br><br><strong>起航远洋原声集</strong><br>Ella van Dyck 创作的全新曲目，同时也提供单独购买的选择。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1811550/extras/03e97ea48dd87872d9eb4a4ad6db81f9.avif?t=1731931053\" width=616 height=616 /></span>",
